data.description: Looking for a lovely lakefront hideaway, nestled within the privacy of 4.4 acres? Very convenient to Roanoke and Westlake, this 4BR/3.5BA home has been lovingly remodeled by the current owners. Main level with large living area, highlighted by a stacked stone fireplace with pellet-stove insert. Spacious kitchen with updated appliances and cabinetry. MBR on main lvl w/ updated bath. Two guest rooms with bath on UL. Lower level set up as an apartment w/ separate entrance, w/d, kitchen, BR and bath. Plenty of deck area leading to large floating dock with slip for pontoon boat. No boat lift, but possibility of installing hydraulic lift in current slip. Plenty of storage with large outbuilding at top of lot and storage shed near house.
